item.title: 4 road trip beauty looks that make you look polished but not high maintenance
item.description:
4 road trip beauty looks that make you look polished but not high maintenance

Victoria Day long weekend is just around the corner and we couldn't be more excited. Aside from some much needed R&R, the long weekend is also a good time to step up our beauty game. Whether we're roughing it outdoors, "glamping" or road-tripping across Canada, we want a look that's effortlessly chic.
